channel.description:
[size=18pt]I know this is OLD but some people still like it :)[/size]
Hmm, My first release.. i did allot u gotta double a certain item [prevents duping i suppose.]
Client link. (updated link) =) http://uppit.com/v/6ZGPZI6B
Server link http://uppit.com/v/Q4R558PU
Commands ::howtobeanpc ::beasoldier ::beacat ::beahellcat ::beapirate ::beazombie ::beaguard ::beagiant ::beabanker ::bearock
theres more in ::howtobeanpc
Theres Customs. such as demon hands [looks like dclaws sorta] demon horns 1 demon horns 2 demon feet demon head demon tail ------------ ladies platelegs ladies platebody ladies chainbody ladies shield ladies sword ladies boots ladies gaunts ----------- this looks like bloody ahrims but its draconic draconic body draconic legs draconic hood ----------- these are in the client also..but u gotta add there ids to the item4.java ^^^^^ invandis platelegs invandis helm invandis chain invandis shield invandis gloves invandis boots invandis sword ------------- lava plate lava legs lava chain lava helm lava shield lava sword lava gaunts lava boots
Well, heres pictures

Epic Skills but as always. OLD every skill worx exept herblore i think my friend coded herblore for me i think [img]http://i452.photobucket.com/albums/qq250/iambanker96/skills.png[/img]
Shawps..but added a chaos alter incase players whine about there prayer lvl being 0. [img]http://i452.photobucket.com/albums/qq250/iambanker96/shops.png[/img]
